---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import co27 from "../../../assets/exco/team-fun.png";
---

<PageLayout title="SSA Berkeley | New Admits">
    <h1>Welcome to Cal</h1>

    <p style="padding-top: 0.5rem; width: 80%; text-align: center;">
        First of all, BIG congratulations! We're excited to have you here at UC
        Berkeley and SSA!
    </p>

    <section>
        <Image
            src={co27}
            alt="Class of 2027"
            style="width: 80%; height: auto; max-width: 800px; min-width: 300px; border-radius: 1rem;"
            loading="eager"
        />
        <p>
            Whether you're an undergraduate first-year, a transfer student, or a
            graduate student, SSA will be the community you need as you begin
            your journey at Cal.
        </p>
        <p>
            From Friendsgiving to CNY, SSA hosts a variety of socials that will
            give you plenty opportunity for meeting other Singaporeans here at
            Cal. You can also look forward to many networking opportunities with
            professionals and students from Singapore and the Bay Area!
        </p>
        <p>
            With so much to offer, we hope that your experience at Cal will
            start on a high note, so be sure to join us!
        </p>
        <a 
            href="https://t.me/Arshul_garz"
            target="_blank"
            class="button"
        >
            Contact us
        </a>
    </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    section {
        width: 80%;
        max-width: 800px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        row-gap: 2rem;
        padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .button {
        color: white;
        background-color: black;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        transition-property: opacity;
        transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        transition-duration: 300ms;
    }

    .button:hover {
        opacity: 0.85;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        section {
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
    }
</style>
